# StyleGenie Project Rules

## Project Structure

StyleGenie is a full-stack AI fashion application with the following architecture:

- **Frontend**: Next.js 14 with TypeScript, located in [frontend/](mdc:frontend/)
- **Backend**: Microservices architecture in [services/](mdc:services/)
  - API Gateway: [services/api-gateway/](mdc:services/api-gateway/)
  - Image Generation: [services/image-generation/](mdc:services/image-generation/)
  - Search Engine: [services/search-engine/](mdc:services/search-engine/)
  - Atelier Matching: [services/atelier-matching/](mdc:services/atelier-matching/)
- **Shared**: Common schemas in [shared/](mdc:shared/)

## Code Conventions

### Frontend
- Use TypeScript for all components
- Follow mobile-first design principles
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling (see [frontend/tailwind.config.ts](mdc:frontend/tailwind.config.ts))
- Components should be in [frontend/components/](mdc:frontend/components/)
- API routes in [frontend/app/api/](mdc:frontend/app/api/)

### Backend
- Use FastAPI for all services
- Follow RESTful API conventions
- Use Pydantic models for request/response validation
- Services communicate via HTTP (see [services/api-gateway/main.py](mdc:services/api-gateway/main.py))

## Key Files

- API Gateway: [services/api-gateway/main.py](mdc:services/api-gateway/main.py)
- Frontend entry: [frontend/app/page.tsx](mdc:frontend/app/page.tsx)
- Docker config: [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml)
- Documentation: [docs/](mdc:docs/)

## AI Integration Points

- Image generation: [services/image-generation/main.py](mdc:services/image-generation/main.py) - integrate SDXL/Flux models
- Vision encoder: [services/search-engine/main.py](mdc:services/search-engine/main.py) - integrate CLIP models
- See [docs/INTEGRATION.md](mdc:docs/INTEGRATION.md) for integration details
